               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280221-141-cd750" type="crimeDate">28th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-141-off749 t18280221-141-cd750"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 3s. the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280221-141-victim885" type="victimName">
                        Peter 
                        Tyler
                     <interp inst="t18280221-141-victim885" type="surname" value="Tyler"></interp>
